{"tid":2321083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊思琦獲李居明鼓勵姊弟戀　追求者個個細十年八載嫌差距大拒愛","createTime":"2020-12-11T09:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T02:24:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7de23e0907d2cffb08ae2acbaaab9432a9986b38","tid":2321083,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"楊思琦應玄學大師李居明邀請，紀念粵劇一百周年電影《粵劇靈》的部份環節，為《梁紅玉擊鼓退金兵》試造型，她會演出幾個粵劇片段，亦將與米雪、賴慰玲一起為該部電影出任主持。<br />\n<br />\n雖然思琦年屈42歲，是兩個小孩之母，不過樣貌身材都keep得好好，近年在內地甚為吃香，前陣子就有多齣古裝劇、時裝劇斟她演出，可惜因疫情關係，劇集多數延期開拍，而她亦無法北上。不過師傅指肖馬的她在來年（牛年）12生肖中排名第一，行紫微龍德星大運，影視齊飛，未來四年會豬籠入水，令思琦開心到彈起。<br />\n<br />\n師傅亦指她旺桃花，牛年流行姐弟戀，鼓勵她勇敢面對，她笑言身邊確實有不少男朋友，只是大部份較她細十年八載，她不能接受姐弟戀，所以都拒絕了，李師傳預言她作為肖馬的代表人物，不但桃花旺，娛樂事業也旺，因此特地安排她在影片中擊鼓，認為可收「擊鼓退瘟疫」之效。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201211/414077076480462848901263.jpeg/GMYAr0YTKnWHjgpBWKNFaoiFGhtWFR7v7SuGeu0rhno?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201211%2F414077076480462848901263.jpeg%2FGMYAr0YTKnWHjgpBWKNFaoiFGhtWFR7v7SuGeu0rhno%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=15ab9e5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20b8db5b9bcb24e18a1c0990796536db5ead29dc","tid":2321083,"uid":6604,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日先話自己有「老公」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883e360259c7a1818ad8bc5e3d67f62df64c855f","tid":2321083,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20b8db5b9bcb24e18a1c0990796536db5ead29dc","tid":2321083,"uid":6604,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日先話自己有「老公」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"人生"},{"pid":"85aa7e2f40e3d396346482bd1b4af64d29b3fadd","tid":2321083,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"真係思覺失調 <br />\n平衡時空幻想左幾多個世界出嚟"},{"pid":"56ce06e4e351e2f6fc45688f716702cf58d50c7c","tid":2321083,"uid":32723,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"有老公都要識男朋友<br />\n<br />\n你都幾淫幾水性楊花喎"},{"pid":"70eddcc8de807528a258f1c89962bd450ece80b6","tid":2321083,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20b8db5b9bcb24e18a1c0990796536db5ead29dc","tid":2321083,"uid":6604,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日先話自己有「老公」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"老公還老公，男朋友還男朋友，兩樣嘢可以同時擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da667ecd2d41d42b349a463c549388a0a09c2b58","tid":2321083,"uid":238301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"等一下 我有老公"},{"pid":"fcd159e163ba93940f011dc9ef116dd7c19a15fc","tid":2321083,"uid":197857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"呢d女好撚噁心<br />\n但佢幾正 唔惹病的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb92ca9a12c2dececa1763cfb77466c3535408d5","tid":2321083,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"咁我有機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a92550a4641933c5c8aa97c614f8dcef489a59f","tid":2321083,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20b8db5b9bcb24e18a1c0990796536db5ead29dc","tid":2321083,"uid":6604,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日先話自己有「老公」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk